xine-lib (1.1.20-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
    - Typos fixed. (Closes: #644927)
    - No longer crashes with some sample WMV files. We think that this was
      an ffmpeg bug. (Closes: #584629)

  * Moved the libxine1-gnome suggestion from libxine1-plugins to
    libxine1-misc-plugins (which can be installed without libxine1-plugins).
  * Added a few names to debian/copyright.
  * Portability fix. (Closes: #634435)

